snippet.title: PlayStation Experience 2015: Paragon - Announce Trailer | PS4
snippet.description:
Paragon, the MOBA from Epic Games, is coming to PS4 in 2016. Paragon puts you in the fight with explosive action, direct third-person control, and deep strategic choice.

Sign up for the beta and learn more at: www.Paragon.com
Twitter: http://www.twitter.com/paragon
Facebook: http://www.facebook.com/paragon

This trailer was captured entirely in Unreal Engine 4.
